{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1709-08_273"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Mort de Messire Chrestien de Lamoignon]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", août 1709 [tome 8], p. 273-276."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La France vient de perdre un de ses ornemens dans la personne de Mre Chrestien de Lamoignon, ancien President à Mortier du Parlement, & honoraire de l’Academie Royale des Medailles & Inscriptions. Il estoit fils de Guillaume de Lamoignon, premier President du Parlement, & de Madeleine Potier, fille de Nicolas Potier Sieur d’Ocquerre, Secretaire d’Etat. Sa naissance, son érudition, & les grands Emplois par lesquels il a passé, fournissent une vaste carriere pour un bel Eloge ; mais comme selon l’usage de cette Academie le Secretaire doit publiquement prononcer un Eloge de ceux qui meurent dans ce Corps, je remets à vous en parler lorsqu’il aura prononcé cet Eloge, ainsi que de sa Maison. Je vous diray cependant que c’est à juste titre que cette Academie l’avoit choisi pour paroistre à sa teste, puisqu’il est peu d’hommes qui ayent eu une plus parfaite connoissance des Medailles antiques, & qu’il avoit conservé du Cabinet de Mr le Premier President son pere, une suite tres belle de Medailles Romaines de grand Bronze. Voicy des Vers qui ont esté faits au sujet de cette mort par Mr Moreau de Mautour de la même Academie."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lamoignon ne vit plus. Ce nom seul dans mon cœur,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Comprend tout son éloge & toute ma douleur."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Pourroit-on exprimer ces nobles caracteres,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "De grandeur, d’équité, de vertu, de douceur."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui dans ce Magistrat furent hereditaires."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Muses & Themis viennent de perdre en luy"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Leur ornement & leur appuy."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Toy, dont il a subi l’Arrest irrevocable,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Déesse aveugle, impitoyable,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu n’as point ménagé ses jours si prétieux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais si nous n’avons fait que d’inutiles vœux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sa memoire du moins, & son nom respectable,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Malgré toy, passeront à nos derniers Neveux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}]}